<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Q: What is the formula to calculate my mana regen from meditation?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
A: At level 60 it has been calculated to add 18mana tick (skill 252). When medding this would give a total of 20 as standing mana regen is 1 per tick, sitting mana regen is 2 per tick.<br>
&lt;Need a formula!&gt;<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Q: Does 'Flowing Thought' (FT) Stack?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
A: Yes. If you have an FT1 item and an FT2 item, you get FT3 total. Furthermore, if you have several FT items of the same level, they too will stack. So FT1+FT1+FT1 will give you a total of 3 extra regen per tick.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Q: Is 'Flowing Thought' capped?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
A: Yes. You can have a maximum of 15 points of FT in total.<br>
<br>
