<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> 12. Player vs. Player (PvP)</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Q: Why do people go on about Shock of Lightening in pvp?</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
